<div class="two-thirds">

        <h1 class="page-title">Tell us who you employ</h1>

        <p>Use this service to:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Give us the personal details of the childcare workers you employ</li>
            <li>Check, change and confirm that the details we currently hold are still up to date</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you’re an Ofsted registered childminder, organisation or setting that provides childcare in Buckinghamshire, you need to give us up-to-date records of the people you employ.</p>

        <h2>How often should I update my records?</h2>

        <p>It’s best to keep your records up to date whenever your employees change.</p>

        <p>You should check your records at least twice a year. Normally this is at the start of each academic term.</p>

        <div class="form-actions">
        <%= link_to "Start now", eligibility_path, class: "button" %>
        </div>
  
        <h2>Before you start</h2>

        <p>You’ll need the account details you use to manage your service in the Family Information Service’s directory.</p>

        <p>If you don’t have an account, you’ll need to <a href="#">register first</a>.</p>
    </main>
